must be both integers or both polynomials, and the result is a
row vector with three components \f(CW\*(C`u\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`v\*(C'\fR, and  \fIgcd\fR \f(CW\*(C`(x,y)\*(C'\fR.
.IX Xref "extended gcd"
.PP
