\&\esubsecidx{chinese}\f(CW\*(C`(x,{y})\*(C'\fR: if \f(CW\*(C`x\*(C'\fR and \f(CW\*(C`y\*(C'\fR are both intmods or both
polmods, creates (with the same type) a \f(CW\*(C`z\*(C'\fR in the same residue class
