.IX Xref "j"
.PP
\  \f(CW\*(C`omega\*(C'\fR :   \f(CW\*(C`[\*(C'\fR\fIomega\fR\f(CW\*(C`_1,\*(C'\fR\fIomega\fR\f(CW\*(C`_2]\*(C'\fR, periods forming a basis of
the complex lattice defining \f(CW\*(C`E\*(C'\fR (\fIomega\fR\f(CW\*(C`_1\*(C'\fR is the
.IX Xref "omega"
.PP
\                   real period, and \fIomega\fR\f(CW\*(C`_2/\*(C'\fR\fIomega\fR\f(CW\*(C`_1\*(C'\fR belongs to
