known to hold in full generality thanks to the work of Breuil,
Conrad, Diamond, Taylor and Wiles). \f(CW\*(C`E\*(C'\fR must be an
\&\fIsell\fR as output by \f(CW\*(C`ellinit\*(C'\fR. For this function
