.IX Xref "akell"
.PP
\&\esubsecidx{ellan}\f(CW\*(C`(E,n)\*(C'\fR: computes the vector of the first \f(CW\*(C`n\*(C'\fR \f(CW\*(C`a_k\*(C'\fR
