output by \f(CW\*(C`ellinit\*(C'\fR, defined over \fBQ\fR, \fBF\fR\f(CW\*(C`_p\*(C'\fR or \fBQ\fR\f(CW\*(C`_p\*(C'\fR. \f(CW\*(C`E\*(C'\fR must be
given by a Weierstrass equation minimal at \f(CW\*(C`p\*(C'\fR.
.PP
