to \fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 0\*(C'\fR, and \efuns{apell2}{E,p} (\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 1\*(C'\fR).
.IX Xref "ellap0"
.PP
\&\esubsecidx{ellbil}\f(CW\*(C`(E,z1,z2)\*(C'\fR: if \f(CW\*(C`z1\*(C'\fR and \f(CW\*(C`z2\*(C'\fR are points on the elliptic
curve \f(CW\*(C`E\*(C'\fR, assumed to be integral given by a minimal model, this function
