\&\esubsecidx{elleisnum}\f(CW\*(C`(E,k,{\*(C'\fR\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 0})\*(C'\fR: \f(CW\*(C`E\*(C'\fR being an elliptic curve as
output by \f(CW\*(C`ellinit\*(C'\fR (or, alternatively, given by a 2\-component vector
\&\f(CW\*(C`[\*(C'\fR\fIomega\fR\f(CW\*(C`_1,\*(C'\fR\fIomega\fR\f(CW\*(C`_2]\*(C'\fR representing its periods), and \f(CW\*(C`k\*(C'\fR being an even
