weight \f(CW\*(C`k\*(C'\fR at \f(CW\*(C`E\*(C'\fR, namely
.PP
\ \ \f(CW\*(C`
(2i \*(C'\fR\fIpi\fR\f(CW\*(C`/\*(C'\fR\fIomega\fR\f(CW\*(C`_2)^k
(1 + 2/\*(C'\fR\fIzeta\fR\f(CW\*(C`(1\-k) \*(C'\fR\fIsum\fR\f(CW\*(C`_{n >= 0} n^{k\-1}q^n / (1\-q^n)),
\&\*(C'\fR
.PP
where \f(CW\*(C`q = e(\*(C'\fR\fIomega\fR\f(CW\*(C`_1/\*(C'\fR\fIomega\fR\f(CW\*(C`_2)\*(C'\fR.
.PP
When \fIflag\fR is non-zero and \f(CW\*(C`k = 4\*(C'\fR or 6, returns the elliptic invariants \f(CW\*(C`g_2\*(C'\fR
or \f(CW\*(C`g_3\*(C'\fR, such that
.PP
\ \ \f(CW\*(C`y^2 = 4x^3 \- g_2 x \- g_3\*(C'\fR
.PP
