\&\*(C'\fR\fIomega\fR\f(CW\*(C`_2]\*(C'\fR
.PP
The library syntax is \fBelleta\fR\f(CW\*(C`(om, \*(C'\fR\fIprec\fR\f(CW\*(C`)\*(C'\fR
.IX Xref "elleta"
