is the generator of the group of roots of unity (\f(CW\*(C`bnf.tu\*(C'\fR), the output is
a vector \f(CW\*(C`[x_1,...,x_r,x_{r+1}]\*(C'\fR such that \f(CW\*(C`x = u_1^{x_1}...
u_r^{x_r}.\*(C'\fR\fIzeta\fR\f(CW\*(C`^{x_{r+1}}\*(C'\fR. The \f(CW\*(C`x_i\*(C'\fR are integers for \f(CW\*(C`i <= r\*(C'\fR and is an
integer modulo the order of \fIzeta\fR for \f(CW\*(C`i = r+1\*(C'\fR.
.PP
The library syntax is \fBisunit\fR\f(CW\*(C`(\*(C'\fR\fIbnf\fR\f(CW\*(C`,x)\*(C'\fR.
.IX Xref "isunit"
.PP
