greater accuracy.
.PP
Note that the member functions are \fInot\fR available for \fIsbnf\fR, you
have to use \f(CW\*(C`bnfmake\*(C'\fR explicitly first.
.PP
The library syntax is \fBmakebigbnf\fR\f(CW\*(C`(\*(C'\fR\fIsbnf\fR\f(CW\*(C`,\*(C'\fR\fIprec\fR\f(CW\*(C`)\*(C'\fR, where \fIprec\fR is a
C long integer.
.IX Xref "makebigbnf"
.PP
