\&\esubsecidx{idealred}\f(CW\*(C`(\*(C'\fR\fInf\fR\f(CW\*(C`,I,{\*(C'\fR\fIvdir\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 0})\*(C'\fR: LLL reduction of
