normal subgroup \f(CW\*(C`H\*(C'\fR such that \f(CW\*(C`G = H\*(C'\fR , or \f(CW\*(C`G/H  ~  A_4\*(C'\fR , or \f(CW\*(C`G/H  ~ 
S_4\*(C'\fR. Abelian and nilpotent groups are WKSS. In practice, almost all groups
of small order are WKSS, the exceptions having order 36(1 exception), 48(2),
56(1), 60(1), 72(5), 75(1), 80(1), 96(10) and \f(CW\*(C` >= 108\*(C'\fR.
.PP
