\&\esubsecidx{nfinit}\f(CW\*(C`(\*(C'\fR\fIpol\fR\f(CW\*(C`,{\*(C'\fR\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 0})\*(C'\fR: \fIpol\fR being a non-constant,
