functions\fR is preferred since the specific data organization specified below
may change in the future. Currently, \f(CW\*(C`nf\*(C'\fR is a row vector with 9
components:
.PP
\&\fInf\fR\f(CW\*(C`[1]\*(C'\fR contains the polynomial \fIpol\fR (\fInf\fR\f(CW\*(C`.pol\*(C'\fR).
