\&\fInf\fR\f(CW\*(C`[3]\*(C'\fR contains the discriminant \f(CWd(K)\fR (\fInf\fR\f(CW\*(C`.disc\*(C'\fR) of \f(CW\*(C`K\*(C'\fR.
.PP
\&\fInf\fR\f(CW\*(C`[4]\*(C'\fR contains the index of \fInf\fR\f(CW\*(C`[1]\*(C'\fR (\fInf\fR\f(CW\*(C`.index\*(C'\fR),
i.e.\ \f(CW\*(C`[\*(C'\fR\fBZ\fR\f(CW\*(C`_K : \*(C'\fR\fBZ\fR\f(CW\*(C`[\*(C'\fR\fItheta\fR\f(CW\*(C`]]\*(C'\fR, where \fItheta\fR is any root of \fInf\fR\f(CW\*(C`[1]\*(C'\fR.
