\&\fInf\fR\f(CW\*(C`[5]\*(C'\fR is a vector containing 7 matrices \f(CW\*(C`M\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`G\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`T2\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`T\*(C'\fR,
\&\f(CW\*(C`MD\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`TI\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`MDI\*(C'\fR useful for certain computations in the number field \f(CW\*(C`K\*(C'\fR.
