\&\esubsecidx{polcompositum}\f(CW\*(C`(P,Q,{\*(C'\fR\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 0})\*(C'\fR: \f(CW\*(C`P\*(C'\fR and \f(CW\*(C`Q\*(C'\fR
