the simple factors of the étale \fBQ\fR\-algebra \f(CW\*(C`A = \*(C'\fR\fBQ\fR\f(CW\*(C`(X, Y) / (P(X), Q(Y))\*(C'\fR.
The factors are given by a list of polynomials \f(CW\*(C`R\*(C'\fR in \fBZ\fR\f(CW\*(C`[X]\*(C'\fR, associated to
the number field \fBQ\fR\f(CW\*(C`(X)/ (R)\*(C'\fR, and sorted by increasing degree (with respect
