\&\esubsecidx{zetak}\f(CW\*(C`(\*(C'\fR\fIznf\fR\f(CW\*(C`,x,{\*(C'\fR\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 0})\*(C'\fR: \fIznf\fR being a number
field initialized by \f(CW\*(C`zetakinit\*(C'\fR (\fInot\fR by \f(CW\*(C`nfinit\*(C'\fR),
computes the value of the Dedekind zeta function of the number
field at the complex number \f(CW\*(C`x\*(C'\fR. If \fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 1\*(C'\fR computes Dedekind \fILambda\fR
