\&\esubsecidx{polroots}\f(CW\*(C`(\*(C'\fR\fIpol\fR\f(CW\*(C`,{\*(C'\fR\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 0})\*(C'\fR: complex roots of the polynomial
