.PP
\&\esubsecidx{matdetint}\f(CW\*(C`(x)\*(C'\fR: \f(CW\*(C`x\*(C'\fR being an \f(CW\*(C`m x n\*(C'\fR matrix with integer
coefficients, this function computes a \fImultiple\fR of the determinant of the
lattice generated by the columns of \f(CW\*(C`x\*(C'\fR if it is of rank \f(CW\*(C`m\*(C'\fR, and returns
