integer.
.IX Xref "isdiagonal"
.PP
\&\esubsecidx{matker}\f(CW\*(C`(x,{\*(C'\fR\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 0})\*(C'\fR: gives a basis for the kernel of the
