.IX Xref "matker0"
.PP
\&\esubsecidx{matkerint}\f(CW\*(C`(x,{\*(C'\fR\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 0})\*(C'\fR: gives an LLL-reduced \fBZ\fR\-basis
