The library syntax is \fBmatsize\fR\f(CW\*(C`(x)\*(C'\fR.
.IX Xref "matsize"
.PP
\&\esubsecidx{matsnf}\f(CW\*(C`(X,{\*(C'\fR\fIflag\fR\f(CW\*(C` = 0})\*(C'\fR: if \f(CW\*(C`X\*(C'\fR is a (singular or non-singular)
