\&\esubsecidx{intfouriersin}\f(CW\*(C`(X = a,b,z,\*(C'\fR\fIexpr\fR\f(CW\*(C`,{\*(C'\fR\fItab\fR\f(CW\*(C`})\*(C'\fR: numerical
integration of \fIexpr\fR\f(CW\*(C`(X)\*(C'\fR \fIsin\fR \f(CW\*(C`(2\*(C'\fR\fIpi\fR\f(CW\*(C` zX)\*(C'\fR from \f(CW\*(C`a\*(C'\fR to \f(CW\*(C`b\*(C'\fR, in other words
